c: 6
v: 19
t: "Say: \"Which is the greatest testimony\" Say: \"God is witness between me and you, and He has inspired to me this Quran that I may warn you with it and whomever it reaches, that you bear witness that along with God are other gods!\"; Say: \"I do not bear witness!\", Say: \"He is only One god, and I am innocent of what you set up"